list.name: Test Start
list.query: SELECT first(*) FROM testStartEnd WHERE status='started' AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter

list.name: Test End
list.query: SELECT last(*) as "test_start" FROM testStartEnd WHERE status='finished' AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter

list.name: Saturation point
list.query: select ath from samples where time > '2016-12-15 18:59:20' limit 1

dashboard.description: This dashboard shows live load test metrics provided by JMeter.

panels.content: The following panels show aggregated metrics for all requests

targets.query: SELECT SUM("difference") FROM (SELECT "startedThreads" - "finishedThreads" as "difference" FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "loadGenerator") WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s)
SELECT  count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null)
SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT 1 - sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("errorCount")/count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT mean("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "errorCount" = 0 AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND "loadGenerator" =~ /^$lg$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation), "requestName" fill(null)

SELECT mean("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "errorCount" = 1 AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND "requestName" =~ /^$request$/ AND "loadGenerator" =~ /^$lg$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation), "responseCode", "requestName" fill(null)

SELECT "startedThreads" - "finishedThreads" FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "loadGenerator" fill(null)

SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "errorCount" = 0 AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation) fill(null)

SELECT SUM("difference") FROM (SELECT last("startedThreads") - last("finishedThreads") as "difference" FROM "virtualUsers" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "loadGenerator") WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(2s) fill(none)

SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "errorCount" = 1 AND "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation) fill(null)
SELECT mean("responseBytes") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation)
SELECT mean("requestBytes") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation)

SELECT count(responseTime) as Count, mean(responseTime)/1000 as Average, median(responseTime)/1000 as Median, percentile(responseTime, 90)/1000 as "90% Line",percentile(responseTime, 95)/1000 as "95% Line",percentile(responseTime, 99)/1000 as "99% Line", min(responseTime)/1000 as Min, max(responseTime)/1000 as Max, (sum(errorCount)/count(responseTime))*100 as "Error Rate", stddev("responseTime") as "Standard Deviation",last(tpsRate) as "Throughput",last(networkRate) as "Network Throughput" FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "requestName"

SELECT mean("connectTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE "projectName" =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/ AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation), "requestName" fill(null)

SELECT count("responseTime") FROM "requestsRaw" WHERE projectName =~ /^$projectID$/ AND "envType" =~ /^$envType$/  AND "testType" =~ /^$testName$/  AND "responseCode" =~ /^$responseCode$/  AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($aggregation), "responseCode" fill(null)
